verbose_text: To further confirm whether Sal B promotes autophagy in HUVECs under oxidative stress, the HUVECs were pre-treated with different concentrations of Sal B (5, 10 and 20 mug/ml), followed by incubation with 800 muM H 2 O 2 for 24 h, and the expression levels of LC3-II, Beclin-1 and p62 were detected.
